These are autogenerated files. Please update the template.

On Tue, Dec 1, 2015, 6:31 PM Jan Tattermusch notifications@github.com
wrote:

> -- upgrades openssl nuget package to 1.0.2d
> -- make openssl, zlib, and csharp.native.ext packages VS2015 ready
> -- include 64bit builds of openssl and zlib in the native packages
> 
> -- when native nuget packages are used in a managed C# project, improve
> the autodetection of what version of .dll gets copied to the output
> directory (autodetect VS version and try to detect Debug/Release
> configuration).
> 
> As of now, tests for this PR will fail because the new nuget packages for
> openssl and zlib haven't been uploaded yet (i'll upload them once I get
> preliminary LGTM for this PR).
> 
> The commit "regenerate project files" contains tons of autogenerated
> 
> ## .vsxproj files, so I recommend reviewing this PR commit-by-commit.
